Important note: This diagram is an extreme simplification and only provides an overview of our website's architecture.
Many dependencies and data flow between modules are not shown because they will over-complicate the diagram.
The missing parts include, but not limited to, the usage of models across the website, the data flow between
the store modules and the models, and the entire data layer.
